                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Exhibition -->
            <div class="nd-panel" data-section="exhibition">
                <div class="nd-panel-header">
                    <span class="nd-panel-tag">Events</span>
                    <h2>Exhibitions</h2>
                    <p>We participate in global industrial exhibitions to showcase TKIL's capabilities.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="nd-cards">
                    <div class="nd-card">
                        <div class="nd-card-year">2025</div>
                        <h3>EXCON – Bengaluru</h3>
                        <p>Showcased latest plant engineering solutions at South Asia's largest construction expo.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="nd-card">
                        <div class="nd-card-year">2026</div>
                        <h3>Hannover Messe</h3>
                        <p>Presenting TKIL's innovation roadmap at the world's leading industrial trade fair.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Brochures -->
            <div class="nd-panel" data-section="brochures">
                <div class="nd-panel-header">
                    <span class="nd-panel-tag">Downloads</span>
                    <h2>Brochures</h2>
                    <p>Download our product and company brochures for detailed information.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="nd-cards">
                    <div class="nd-card nd-card-download">
                        <div class="nd-card-icon">📘</div>
                        <h3>Company Profile</h3>
                        <p>Full overview of TKIL's history, capabilities, and global footprint.</p>
