                    </div>
                    <div class="nd-card nd-card-download">
                        <div class="nd-card-icon">📗</div>
                        <h3>Product Catalogue 2025</h3>
                        <p>Detailed listing of all engineering products and plant solutions.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="nd-download-btn">Download PDF</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="nd-card nd-card-download">
                        <div class="nd-card-icon">📙</div>
                        <h3>EPC Capabilities</h3>
                        <p>In-depth brochure on TKIL's end-to-end EPC project delivery model.</p>
